					small 1,2


				img(src="img/tab-2.jpg", alt="")
				.smallest.text-left 1. Dunlop SP., Jenkins&nbsp;D., Spiller RS. Distinctive clinical, psychological and histological features of&nbsp;postinfectious irritable bowel syndrome. American J&nbsp;Gastroenterology 2003; 98 (7):1578&nbsp;&mdash; 1583. 
					br
					| 2. Tazume&nbsp;S., Ozawa&nbsp;A., Yamamoto&nbsp;T. et&nbsp;al. Ecological study on&nbsp;the intestinal bacteria flora of&nbsp;patients with diarrhea. Clin Infect Dis 1993; 16&nbsp;(l&nbsp;2):77-82)
			+e.content.text-center
				img(src="img/tab-3.jpg", alt="")
	// end s-tabs